cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with incorporating syntax into Neural Machine Translation. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses ensembles and training procedures. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with improving machine translation. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are less likely but still possible categories as they both involve neural networks and machine learning techniques.
